snippet.title: Deadeye Deepfake Simulacrum: Secret Admirer Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello agents. (✿◕‿◕) Deadeye Deepfake Simulacrum is a game about hacking computers, people, even individual bullets! :O We got guns and shootin, we got DEEP character customization, we got the lo-fi hip hop beats (ﾉ◕ヮ◕)ﾉ*:･ﾟ✧ Don’t you wanna complete challenging open ended missions that accommodate your super special personal playstyle? What about confronting technological horrors in the shadows of the far future? What about a crazy story?? You’re gonna finish this game and think “wow that was the CRAZIEST story, what the hecc just happened???”

I worked really *really* hard on this (◕//◕), but I don’t know if anyone is gonna wishlist it on Steam! 
(╥﹏╥)

Unless…

Maybe YOU could wishlist it on Steam for me?? (✿˵◕‿◕˵)
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1545990/Deadeye_Deepfake_Simulacrum/

and be my friend on twitter…? 
https://twitter.com/deaddeepsim

maybe join our discord server even…?
https://discord.gg/Jvv3kU8TKS
